\newlabel{tab:dgm-check}{{1}{26}{DGM-style distinction memory versus backpropagation on a limited online contextual-XOR stream. Offline backprop is a batch upper bound. The relevant runtime comparison is between online backpropagation and online distinction refinement. The distinction-memory run has monotone local scoring-objective decrease at accepted refinements in all runs}{table.caption.13}{}}
